# Development Workflow

## Local Development
- Use local web server for development (Python: `python -m http.server 8000`)
- Test all interactive features in browser
- Validate JSON data structure before deployment
- Check responsive design on multiple screen sizes

## Asset Pipeline
1. Create individual icon files in `icons/16x16/`
2. Use [Rename-Icons.ps1](mdc:Rename-Icons.ps1) for batch renaming
3. Generate sprite sheets using the assembler utility
4. Update JSON metadata files
5. Test in [visual-asset-library.html](mdc:visual-asset-library.html)

## Quality Assurance
- Verify all icons load correctly
- Test search and filtering functionality
- Ensure metadata accuracy
- Validate sprite sheet positioning
- Check cross-browser compatibility

## Deployment
- Commit changes to git repository
- Push to GitHub Pages for automatic deployment
- Verify live site functionality
- Update documentation as needed